Publishing to the Azure Container Registry - Resources
The following commands can be used as a reference to the previous chapter

1. Install the Azure command line interface

https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/install-azure-cli-linux?pivots=apt

2. Login into Azure

sudo az login

3. Login in your repository - Mention the name, user name and password accordingly.

sudo az acr login --name  --username --password

4. Tag your repository

sudo docker tag sqlapp appregistry10002313.azurecr.io/sqlapp

5. Push the image to the repository

sudo docker push appregistry10002313.azurecr.io/sqlapp